T02TD3541E:180b-1: shr'i ma na ma h'a k'a la s'a dha nam /
T02TD3541E:180b-3: dpal ldan nag po chen po'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD3541E:180b-4: dpal ldan mgon po chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3541E:180b-5: de bzhin du sngon du gsungs pa'i rim pas stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes la sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma la h'um yig nag po /
T02TD3541E:180b-6: de yongs su gyur pa las dpal ldan rje btsun nag po chen po phyag gnyis pa /
T02TD3541E:180b-9: spyan gsum pa 'bar ba chen po //
T02TD3541E:180b-10: phyag g-yas pa dang g-yon pa dag gis gri gug dang thod pa bsnams pa /
T02TD3541E:180b-11: mgo bo'i phreng ba'i do shal gyis sku brgyan pa /
T02TD3541E:180b-12: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du brdzes pa /
T02TD3541E:180b-13: mche ba gtsigs pas 'jigs par byed pa /
T02TD3541E:180b-14: sku thams cad la sbrul gyis brgyan pa'o /
T02TD3541E:180b-16: zhal nas khrag 'dzag pa'i bdag nyid du skad cig gis bskyed nas sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3541E:180b-18: aom ma h'a k'a la h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD3541E:180b-21: yungs kar rnams kyis nag po chen po'i spos phul nas sran ma sha dang 'dzum bu ti ka dang chang dang me tog dang byug pa lnga'i lcags kyu'i bdud rtsis nag po chen po mchod pa bya ste /
T02TD3541E:180b-23: aom ma h'a k'a l'a ya sh'a sa no pa k'a ri nam ae sh'a pashtsi ma ka lo aa yam aidam ratna tra y'a pa k'a ri nam ya di pra ti dzny'am sma ra si ta d'a ai dam dushta kha kha kh'a hi kh'a hi ma ra ma ra grihna grihna bandha bandha /
T02TD3541E:180b-27: d'i na me ke na m'a ra ya h'um h'um phat phat tsha ba gsum gyis bsgrub bya'i gzugs byas te lus la tsher mas dgang zhing dug dang ske tshe rnams kyis cho ga bzhin du byugs nas me la bsro bar bya'o //
T02TD3541E:180b-28: gang gi ming dang bcas pa de //
T02TD3541E:180b-29: de bzhin skad cig mthong bar 'gyur //
T02TD3541E:180b-30: slob dpon zhe sdang rtag khro gang //
T02TD3541E:180b-31: gang zhig dkon mchog gsum po dang //
T02TD3541E:180b-32: dpag med sems can rnams 'tshe rnams //
T02TD3541E:180b-33: nag po chen pos za bar byed //
T02TD3541E:180b-34: de yi lus la sha gcod cing //
T02TD3541E:180b-35: de bzhin khrag ni 'thung bar byed //
T02TD3541E:180b-36: spyi bor thig le byas nas gus pa rgya chen po byas nas bzlas par bya'o //
T02TD3541E:180b-37: dpal ldan nag po chen po'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
